{"tid":1892260,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"連登大辯論有無得諗？","createTime":"2020-02-22T11:49:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-28T14:07:24.000Z","uid":221035,"like":97,"dislike":31,"uniUserReply":65,"replies":[{"pid":"46fa89e302a5a9ef5db689c4089edbeeeba9a438","tid":1892260,"uid":221035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T11:49:05.000Z","msg":"連登9屌風氣盛行<br />\n經常有人單單打打互相標籤<br />\n輕易話人係五毛、分化、泛民打手之類，極不健康<br />\n屌走曬啲人<br />\n<br />\n連登本來就係一個討論區，點解唔認認真真嚟場辯論呢？<br />\n當然唔係要互相抓錯處同屌人<br />\n真係想有理性討論，互相用理據說服<br />\n定啲簡單規制，例如唔準9屌同label人<br />\n<br />\n其實一路有好多分歧需要整理同討論<br />\n互相促進下大家諗野<br />\n<br />\n淺黃vs深黃<br />\n和理非vs勇武<br />\n體制內vs體制外<br />\n泛民vs本土<br />\n溫和vs激進<br />\n攬炒vs改革<br />\n港獨vs一國兩制<br />\n<br />\n大家覺得有無得諗？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />認認真真理性討論下真係幾好<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />樓主on99"},{"pid":"f65b5890212bebce570996f5609374fbc20ddad8","tid":1892260,"uid":263563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T11:49:25.000Z","msg":"有"},{"pid":"d519ab73ebd5e65874223b214a50777863b2e9f7","tid":1892260,"uid":221035,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T11:49:26.000Z","msg":"大家如果覺得可行，可以suggest下辯題"},{"pid":"4f99a73bfa11ff969b2bc293af36d2e066b4c501","tid":1892260,"uid":221035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T11:49:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38a4ffd61a0d1856994972d6de8f112d0597e284","tid":1892260,"uid":31215,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T11:50:35.000Z","msg":"有得諗vs冇得諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33c2c8dfd3bf2fc8798fa83b5f3d871e9bfd1bcb","tid":1892260,"uid":86509,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T11:50:54.000Z","msg":"好耐之前有人講過全民辯論添啦<br />\n文藝復興咁"},{"pid":"f2ed0230684f83b72451121a31ecf3d2ce6dce9e","tid":1892